rzy Fedkowicz. Around the same time Piasecki became acquainted with Jerzy Kossak, the son of the best Polish horse painter, Wojciech Kossak, and his future teacher. After graduating he settled in Górny Śląsk. From 1956 to 1962 Piasecki worked as a graphic artist for the magazine ‘Panorama’, while he also established himself as a history painter. In 1974 he emigrated with his family to Austria, where he settled in Vienna. Since then he has mainly focused on depictions of battle and horse scenes. The painting measures 20\" wide X 24\" high. The total measurement of the painting and frame is 28\" wide X 32\" high',3500,1,1,'','',NULL,'2017-07-18 18:05:46','2017-08-08 15:44:07'),(32,'a0031','Natalie Frieda','1981 Lemont IL 60439\nThe painting measures 48\" wide X 24\" high. The total measurement of the painting and frame is 54.5\" wide X 30.5\" high',5000,1,1,'','',NULL,'2017-07-18 18:10:11','2017-08-08 15:36:33'),(33,'a0033','Honezhnom','damaged with wine\nThe painting measures 36\" wide X 24\" high. The total measurement of the painting and frame is 44\" wide X 32\" high',3000,1,1,'','',NULL,'2017-07-18 18:14:48','2017-08-08 15:47:53'),(34,'a0034','Idell Ellingwood','Idell was born in Crawfordsville, Indiana, on January 8, 1920. She was the daughter of the late Claude T. and Jewel (Clore) Mitchell. Idell was a life resident of the Wallace community and had attended Wallace School.\nIdell was a homemaker and artist. She was a former member of the Danville Illinois Art League. She was a member of the Wallace Christian Church. Idell was an accomplished artist. She had her paintings displayed in all 50 states and 3 continents.The painting measures 48\" wide X 24\" high. The total measurement of the painting and frame is 55.5\" wide X 31.5\" high',6000,1,1,'','',NULL,'2017-07-18 18:19:12','2017-08-08 16:30:52'),(35,'a0035','A. Sluvs','The painting measures 48\" wide X 24\" high. The total measurement of the painting and frame is 55\" wide X 31\" high',7000,1,1,'','',NULL,'